## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-102">这`enum`指定的事件类型时引发的事件<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-102">This `enum` specifies the event type when an event is raised for an <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-103">修改 XML 树的所有操作将都细分为一系列的基元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-103">All operations that modify the XML tree break down to a series of primitives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-104">有四种类型的基元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-104">There are four types of primitives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-105">两个基元 （添加和删除） 将作用于集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-105">Two of the primitives (Add and Remove) act on collections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-106">两个 （名称和值） 对实例进行操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-106">Two of them (Name and Value) act on instances.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-107">没有为每个这些基元对应的事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-107">There is a corresponding event for each of these primitives.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-108">修改 XML 树中其中一个事件，因为执行此操作可能会导致意外结果时，您一定要小心。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-108">You should be careful when modifying an XML tree within one of these events, because doing this might lead to unexpected results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-109">例如，如果你收到<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing>事件，并在处理该事件时从树中删除节点，不可能会收到<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-109">For example, if you receive a <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing> event, and while the event is being processed you remove the node from the tree, you might not receive the <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-110">处理事件时，它是有效地修改 XML 树，而不是包含正在接收事件; 的节点是修改同一树所做的修改不会影响在其引发事件的特定节点提供更有效的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-110">When an event is being processed, it is valid to modify an XML tree other than the one that contains the node that is receiving the event; it is even valid to modify the same tree provided the modifications do not affect the specific nodes on which the event was raised.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-111">但是，如果修改包含接收事件的节点的区域，那么你接收的事件和对树的影响是树的不确定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-111">However, if you modify the area of the tree that contains the node receiving the event, the events that you receive and the impact to the tree are undefined.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-112">下面的示例通过将元素添加到树中引发事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-112">The following example raises an event by adding an element to the tree.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root", "content");  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Add(new XElement("Child", "child content"));  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-113">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-113">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Add  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Add  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-114">下面的示例通过从树中移除一个元素引发事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-114">The following example raises an event by removing an element from the tree.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
    new XElement("Child", "content")  
);  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Element("Child").Remove();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-115">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-115">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Remove  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Remove  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-116">下面的示例通过更改元素的名称来引发事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-116">The following example raises an event by changing the name of an element.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root", "content");  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Name = "NewName";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-117">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-117">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Name  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Name  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-118">下面的示例通过设置属性的值来引发事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-118">The following example raises an event by setting the value of an attribute.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
    new XAttribute("Att", "att value")  
);  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.FirstAttribute.Value = "new contents";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3cbec-119">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3cbec-119">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XAttribute  
  Changing: Value  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XAttribute  
  Changed: Value  
```
